  "page": "Rolland Uffering",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Uffering\" title=\"House Uffering\"><img alt=\"House Uffering.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/13/House_Uffering.svg/50px-House_Uffering.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/13/House_Uffering.svg/75px-House_Uffering.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/13/House_Uffering.svg/100px-House_Uffering.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Rolland Uffering</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Uffering\" title=\"House Uffering\"><img alt=\"House Uffering.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/13/House_Uffering.svg/50px-House_Uffering.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/13/House_Uffering.svg/75px-House_Uffering.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/13/House_Uffering.svg/100px-House_Uffering.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rolland Uffering by Lopata 4.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e4/Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg/350px-Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e4/Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg/525px-Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e4/Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg/700px-Rolland_Uffering_by_Lopata_4.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Rolland by Lopata Four</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Uffering\" title=\"House Uffering\">House Uffering</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafrolland_uffering.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafrolland_uffering.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_210_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">210&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nDaughter (possibly)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Issue_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Issue-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Rolland Uffering</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Uffering\" title=\"House Uffering\">House Uffering</a> during the reign of <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a>. He was Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>'s fourth husband.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolland_Uffering&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser Rolland Uffering was the fourth husband of Lady Rohanne Webber of <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a>. His sister was Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Helicent_Uffering\" title=\"Helicent Uffering\">Helicent Uffering</a>. Ser Rolland and his wife had not been married long when he died during the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Spring_Sickness\" title=\"Great Spring Sickness\">Great Spring Sickness</a>. After his death, his sister remained at Coldmoat, as the kin of other deceased husbands of Lady Rohanne had done before her. It was rumored after his death that Rohanne killed him, possibly by poison, as she supposedly had multiple husbands before him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolland_Uffering&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>My husbands seldom linger long, I fear. The last <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Spring_Sickness\" title=\"Great Spring Sickness\">died in the spring</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Helicent_Uffering\" title=\"Helicent Uffering\">Helicent</a> was sister to Ser Rolland Uffering, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne's</a> fourth husband, who <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Spring_Sickness\" title=\"Great Spring Sickness\">died in the spring</a>. My brother was his predecessor, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Staunton\" title=\"Simon Staunton\">Simon Staunton</a>, who had the great misfortune to choke upon a chicken bone. <a href=\"/index.php/Coldmoat\" title=\"Coldmoat\">Coldmoat</a> crawls with revenants, it must be said. The husbands die yet their kin remain, to drink my lady's wines and eat her sweetmeats, like a plague of plump pink <a href=\"/index.php/Locust\" title=\"Locust\">locusts</a> done up in silk and velvet.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Sefton_Staunton\" title=\"Sefton Staunton\">Sefton</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolland_Uffering&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Issue-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Issue_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is currently unknown if <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>'s daughter is by <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Staunton\" title=\"Simon Staunton\">Simon Staunton</a>, her third husband, or Rolland, her fourth.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolland_Uffering&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafrolland_uffering.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafrolland_uffering.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Rolland Uffering.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404050533\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.096 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.322 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 679/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10777/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9118/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1670/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2147/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.210/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.56 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  307.649      1 -total\n 96.83%  297.905      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.25%  296.108      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.96%   36.796     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.36%   19.577      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.43%   10.557      4 Template:Ref\n  2.56%    7.875      2 Template:Date\n  2.02%    6.225      4 Template:Ref/core\n  1.20%    3.694      2 Template:Quote\n  1.03%    3.177      2 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3475-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404050533 and revision id 334838\n -->\n",
